The syndicate has spread its tentacles to land offices in the region.Several cases have been reported of land owners being swindled out of their property. Cartels involved in fraudulent land transactions in Busia County are continually conning unsuspecting land owners out of their property as buyers lose millions of shillings.
The syndicate has spread its tentacles to land offices in the region, with elderly members of society being targeted as they are more easily duped.



